I found a concrete gap: `evidence` payloads in frame-term metadata are currently ignored whenever `matched_terms` is present, so their frame features never become audited ontology terms. I’m patching `codec.py` to treat `evidence` as a first-class metadata value source, then adding targeted regression tests.
